            <title><![CDATA[习近平：希望民企放心大胆发展]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="/s3/files/styles/article_large_full/public/2021-04/001_7.jpg?itok=uu1tOOX-" title="习近平昨天前往广西柳州螺蛳粉生产集聚区考察调研。（新华社微博）" alt="习近平昨天前往广西柳州螺蛳粉生产集聚区考察调研。（新华社微博）" src="https://www.zaobao.com/s3/files/styles/article_large_full/public/2021-04/001_7.jpg?itok=uu1tOOX-" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
